 rates every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the premium index methodology. The exchange caps funding rates at ±2% per interval to prevent extreme funding costs. Funding payments occur automatically between long and short position holders, with the rate determined by the 8-hour time-weighted average premium of the perpetual contract over the spot price. Bitget's fast token listing approach means SUI funding rates can be volatile during major ecosystem announcements."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
